  "title": "Locum Pharmacists Technicians Needed!! #HCGT",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p><p>- Processes prescriptions and dispenses medications to polyclinic patients in accordance with doctor’s directions as specified in\nprescriptions</p><p>- Supports Medication Delivery Service (MDS) and PILBOX\nservice for remote collection of medications</p><p>- Provides Tele-dispensing services (where applicable)</p><p>- Assists in video consultation (VC) and medication\nreconciliation</p><p>Requirements</p><p>- GCE ‘O’ Level with a Certificate in Pharmacy Technician Course (under MOH, PSS\nor its equivalent) or a Diploma in Pharmaceutical Science </p><p>- at least 1 year of pharmacy technician experience<br /><br /><br />All qualified\napplicants, please send in your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p>Tricia Celestine Goh (R1981653)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd | Company\nReg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599 </p>",
